{"tid":427693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣忘記一個人？","createTime":"2017-10-07T15:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T09:14:13.000Z","uid":69088,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdc649d7eed345b972afde9b29f015ad5b139bd","tid":427693,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"有咩撚野方法可以忘記一個人？<br />\n<br />\n試過不斷做野，做到好忙會有一刻可以解脫<br />\n但始終會累，停低又再諗起大家一齊日子<br />\n<br />\n悶的時間可以狂sd無聊野炸對方<br />\n依家有野只可以自己笑<br />\n再無人可以分享⋯"},{"pid":"3dddc2d56a49394f74d1593cae4f66ec7a538312","tid":427693,"uid":40847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"唔好停 覺都唔好訓 不斷做嘢"},{"pid":"4d0b4775c10359fd4f7a6b8d3a12a27ca7b2854a","tid":427693,"uid":59702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"時間啦 唔洗逼自己唔諗 你越唔去越諗 啲畫面仲出嚟<br />\n<br />\n分左手就嚟兩個月了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84116c21c62cf22170efd2fb46171fded2be39cb","tid":427693,"uid":69088,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好停 覺都唔好訓 不斷做嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時手機響一響，會以為佢<br />\n點知拎上手，只係同事<br />\n<br />\n放工忍不住行佢經常出現的地方<br />\n等左好耐都唔見<br />\n<br />\n係咁做野同時，突然浮起一D對話<br />\n會忍不住眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n當你開wtapp、tg發現第一頁已經再見唔到佢<br />\n先發覺原來真正失去左佢<br />\n⋯"},{"pid":"61e3cfbb812894155e26e4f68771130331b4ba05","tid":427693,"uid":6869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8e40bdd784861b8b13369e4ff65ab1c6e319c0c","tid":427693,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間啦 唔洗逼自己唔諗 你越唔去越諗 啲畫面仲出嚟<br />\n<br />\n分左手就嚟兩個月了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打定爸打？<br />\n你分手係一刀切？"},{"pid":"cc0f5a2feaa1747860e7b49a8b4ea31ab0c594f7","tid":427693,"uid":69088,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,